description: This file defines a React functional component 'Navbar' that renders a top navigation bar with links that vary depending on user authentication status. It also handles logout functionality via a data service and navigation.

methods.name: Navbar({ user })
methods.description: React functional component that renders the navigation bar, with user-dependent links and logout functionality.

methods.name: onLogout
methods.description: Asynchronous handler that calls dataService.logout and then navigates to the login page.
